药物联合使用，以更快地控制症状。此外，锂盐在预防双相情感障碍的复发方面也表现出显著效果。\n\n然而，锂盐的治疗窗口较窄，需要密切监测血药浓度，以避免毒性反应。其可能引起严重的药物不良反应，如木僵缄默综合征，且此类不良反应的死亡率较高，预后不良。因此，在使用锂盐时，医生需谨慎评估患者的个体情况，并定期进行监测，以确保治疗的安全性和有效性。", "医生:\"医生\" refers to medical professionals who are trained to diagnose and treat patients, manage adverse drug reactions, and provide comprehensive care. They may have previously treated patients and are often a valuable source of information regarding a patient’s medical history. Their role encompasses both the treatment of current medical conditions and the management of ongoing health concerns, ensuring a holistic approach to patient care.", "直立性低血压:A common adverse reaction to phenothiazines and tricyclic antidepressants, characterized by a sudden drop in blood pressure upon standing", "药物性皮炎:An allergic reaction to psychiatric medications, which can progress to severe conditions like exfoliative dermatitis", "恶性综合征:A rare but severe adverse reaction to high-potency antipsychotics or polypharmacy, characterized by severe extrapyramidal symptoms, fever, and autonomic instability", "粒细胞缺乏症:A serious condition associated with clozapine use, marked by a sudden drop in white blood cell count and increased risk of infection", "锂盐中毒:A condition resulting from lithium toxicity, with symptoms ranging from mild tremors to severe neurological and renal impairment", "剥脱性皮炎:A severe form of drug-induced dermatitis that can result from adverse reactions to psychiatric medications", "日光性皮炎:A type of dermatitis caused by exposure to sunlight, often exacerbated by certain medications like phenothiazines", "锥体外系症状:锥体外系症状（Extrapyramidal Symptoms, EPS）是一组与抗精神病药物相关的运动障碍副作用。这些症状主要影响患者的运动控制能力，可能表现为肌肉僵硬、震颤、运动迟缓或异常不自主运动等。在某些严重情况下，锥体外系症状可能发展为神经阻滞剂恶性综合征（Neuroleptic Malignant Syndrome, NMS），这是一种罕见但可能危及生命的并发症。为了缓解这些症状，医生有时会使用抗震颤药物或其他对症治疗手段。总体而言，锥体外系症状是抗精神病药物治疗中需要密切监测和管理的常见不良反应之一。"], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-v3"}}}